title: 168. Nat Amoore with Adrian Beck: The Power Of Positive Power
itunes:author: Words and Nerds: Authors, books and literature.
itunes:summary: Author Nat Amoore chats to Dani Vee and Adrian Beck about her new book The Power of Positive Pranking. We also prank three of our favourite authors Jack Heath, Tristan Bancks and Amelia McInerney. Do they fall for our nonsense? Listen now on iTunes, Soundcloud and Spotify.
